########### INSTALLATION #############

To install this software type in bash shell :

'sudo ./Configure.sh'

This will configure your computer for installation
Basically it moves or removes some file for installation. 

Then type :

'sudo ./Configure.sh install'

This will 
You must write the sudo prefix because of 
'apt-get install' calling. Open the script and take 
a look to be sure.

'qmake -o makefile isingmodel.pro'

'make'

########### LAUNCH IT !!! ############

You can launch it via :

'isingmodel'

Alone it just show you the usage. You must options to 
run it!

########## UNINSTALLATION ############

This will only clean the file installed that you 
won't need anymore, then type :

>./Configure uninstall

